There are people who will die
Without a heart

11:00.300 --> 11:02.100
Or lungs.

11:02.100 --> 11:06.900
And they will only see your son
As someone who saved their life.

11:06.900 --> 11:10.000
But will they know?

11:10.000 --> 11:14.000
That's not something you need
To worry about right now.

11:15.800 --> 11:18.700
I don't think i want them
To know.

11:20.300 --> 11:22.800
You'll know,
Mrs. Donner.

11:26.400 --> 11:28.400
You'll know.

