13:04.100 --> 13:06.300
His blood pressure
Is dropping.

13:06.300 --> 13:08.200
We need to start him
On dopamine

13:08.200 --> 13:11.200
And give him two more units
Of red blood cells.

13:11.200 --> 13:13.900
But we've already given him
So much blood.

13:13.900 --> 13:16.600
We need to treat him like
Any other living patient.

13:16.600 --> 13:19.000
In order to keep his organs
In perfect condition,

13:19.000 --> 13:20.100
We need to care for him

13:20.100 --> 13:22.400
Like we would someone
Who was still alive.

13:26.200 --> 13:27.900
<i>don't think too much
About what he did.</i>

13:27.900 --> 13:29.400
<i>just think about
What he can do.</i>

13:29.400 --> 13:31.600
I'm trying.
It's just that --

13:31.600 --> 13:34.100
Gunshot wounds to the head
Are notoriously unstable.

13:34.100 --> 13:36.100
We need to keep very close tabs
On him.

13:36.100 --> 13:37.000
Believe me,

13:37.000 --> 13:39.700
We're the only people
In this hospital who will.

13:39.700 --> 13:42.000
I think i screwed up
With the yorks.

13:42.000 --> 13:43.200
I think i blew it.

13:43.200 --> 13:44.000
What happened?

13:44.000 --> 13:46.500
It was going fine,
And then i said,

13:46.500 --> 13:50.500
"even though three people died
Today, if they all donate,

13:50.700 --> 13:54.400
Dozens could get a chance
To live."

13:54.400 --> 13:55.900
You said, "if they all."

13:55.900 --> 13:59.200
Oh, i mean,
It just went so quiet.

13:59.200 --> 14:01.200
Why is that so bad?

14:01.200 --> 14:03.300
Well, they know we're trying
To get duane donner's organs.

14:03.300 --> 14:05.900
I think
They know that now.

14:05.900 --> 14:07.400
Okay.
I'm gonna go talk to them.

14:07.400 --> 14:09.200
You stay with mr. Donner,
And let me know

14:09.200 --> 14:11.400
