15:42.500 --> 15:44.600
Nothing.

15:44.600 --> 15:46.100
Nothing. Um...

15:47.800 --> 15:49.800
Really good work, teddy.

15:49.800 --> 15:51.000
Thanks.

15:51.800 --> 15:53.800
