16:02.000 --> 16:03.600
Tom: we found a donor.

16:05.400 --> 16:08.100
So we'll take you upstairs,
Prep you for surgery.

16:08.100 --> 16:10.900
And once we take a look
At the donor's liver --

16:10.900 --> 16:12.900
