That it'll work --

16:12.900 --> 16:15.900
Did you find a recipient?

16:15.900 --> 16:17.300
We did.

16:17.800 --> 16:19.800
Is it a child?

16:19.800 --> 16:22.400
No, he was a man
In his 50s.

16:22.400 --> 16:25.400
Does he have a family?

16:25.400 --> 16:26.800
No.

16:31.600 --> 16:35.300
All the same, he gets
Another chance like me.

16:36.100 --> 16:37.800
I hear you.

16:40.900 --> 16:42.700
Excuse me.

16:47.600 --> 16:48.400
So, what is it?

16:48.400 --> 16:50.800
